\section*{Concise Answers: Sampling and Surveys Exercises}
\begin{enumerate}[label=\textbf{4.1.\arabic*}]
\item Population: local businesses; Sample: 150; Respondents: 73.
\item Population: 45,000; Sample: 1,000; Respondents: 137; Issue: nonresponse bias.
\item Voluntary response; biased, strong opinion.
\item No; voluntary response bias.
\item Self-selection; unknown frame; multiple votes; bias.
